metadata.name: cordova-plugin-x-toast
metadata.author: Eddy Verbruggen <eddyverbruggen@gmail.com> (https://github.com/EddyVerbruggen)
metadata.description: This plugin allows you to show a Toast. A Toast is a little non intrusive buttonless popup which automatically disappears.

metadata.name: term-size
metadata.author: Sindre Sorhus <sindresorhus@gmail.com> (sindresorhus.com)
metadata.description: Reliably get the terminal window size (columns & rows)
